## P3.21 Cleanup Service Race Condition — FIXED

### Problem
- cleanup.go:78-96 had race condition
- Lock released between checking 'running' flag and closing 'stopCh'
- Concurrent Stop() calls could both pass the check before either closes channel
- Second close would panic

### Solution
- Added 'stopOnce sync.Once' field to CleanupService struct
- Modified Stop() to use stopOnce.Do() for channel close
- Modified Start() to reset stopOnce for new run cycles
- Captured channel references while holding lock before releasing

### Files Changed
- internal/state/cleanup.go: Added stopOnce field, modified Start/Stop
- internal/state/cleanup_test.go: Added TestCleanupService_ConcurrentStop

